.git
.idea
.nuxt
.output
# Exclude NESTED build artifacts too — root-level patterns don't match nested
# paths, so without these each service's stale services/*/.output gets COPYed
# into the image and shipped instead of a fresh build (caused phantom "missing
# route" deploys).
**/.nuxt
**/.output
**/.nitro
node_modules
**/node_modules
npm-debug.log*
Dockerfile
docker-compose.yml
DEPLOYMENT_*.md
README.md

.claude
.agents
.impeccable.md